Package: forecasthistogram
Type: Package
Title: Functions for handling histogram-type forecasts in economic survey data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Fabian Krüger, Lora Pavlova
Maintainer: Fabian Krüger <fabian.krueger83@gmail.com>
Description: The package accompanies the working paper `Quantifying Subjective 
    Uncertainty in Survey Expectations' (2020, <doi:https://doi.org/10.18452/21401>). Besides
    the method proposed therein, the package also implements the benchmark quantification
    method by Engelberg, Manski and Williams (2009, <doi:https://doi.org/10.1198/jbes.2009.0003>).
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Imports: dplyr, ggplot2, magrittr
